  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This post market outcome study will look at the therapeutic results of the Salto Talaris
      Anatomic ankle prosthesis. The study population will consist of patients who will undergo an
      ankle arthroplasty procedure with a Salto Talaris ankle implant. An analysis will be
      conducted of the results, complications and revisions of this prosthesis based on the
      etiology for which the ankle arthroplasty was performed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, multi-center study that will capture the therapeutic results of the
      Salto Talaris Anatomic ankle prosthesis in the treatment of various ankle afflictions.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
